Quake continued to drive forward.  Not even listening to Apeface, he talked to Tiptop.  "You know, that name Quake was good enough on Cybertron, but here i need a new one. How bout Tremor."

"Sounds cool to me"

"Right on" he said as Tremor plowed into the tree Apeface was on.  "Apeface, report back to base to see if they had heard anything."
